<p><strong>标题：</strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-3103" target="_blank">SCP-3103 - 复仇之翼</a><br />
<strong>作者：</strong>©︎<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/badger100" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3296047); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3296047&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1605673624" alt="Badger100" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3296047)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/badger100" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3296047); return false;">Badger100</a></span><br />
<strong>创作时间：</strong>2017年9月28日<br />
<strong>译者：</strong>©︎<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/achsab" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4325914); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4325914&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1605673624" alt="achsab" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4325914)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/achsab" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4325914); return false;">achsab</a></span></p>
</div>
